org.biopax.paxtools.io.sif.level3

Interface InteractionRuleL3

  • All Superinterfaces:
    InteractionRule
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ComponentRule, ConsecutiveCatalysisRule, ControlRule, ControlsTogetherRule, ExpressionRule, InteractionRuleL3Adaptor, ParticipatesRule

    public interface InteractionRuleL3
extends InteractionRule
    This interface defines a rule which can be run on BioPAX model L2 to derive simple interactions. All new rules should implement this interface.
    Author:
    Emek Demir, Ozgun Babur
